To use remind, use the command:
;remind

To add a reminder for a task you can indicate it when you are adding a task.

e.g. 
;add Buy eggs ;remind DD MM YYYY HH mm am/pm

You can add reminder to task which are already added.

e.g. 
To change reminder of a task with ID = 3
;edit 3 ;remind DD MM YYYY HH mm am/pm